705226f-a.title: Brooklyn: Kings Highway - Bedford Avenue
705226f-a.text:
2519 Kings Highway, north side, between Bedford Ave., and East 26th
Street, showing the Patrick Whalen house, occupied by him in 1873, and still
being occupied by his daughter.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
